SwitchBlade saw the incoming missles and leapt from the side of the building
causeing them to impact into the side. Debris struck the Cybrats leader in
the back forcing him down. He regained his composure seeing the Dinobot
commander flying towards him. He flipped two blades out of his wrists (Hence
the name) "So the bot wants to play chicken with me?" he dusted the last of
the debris off of his shoulder glareing at the incoming bot. With one last
observation about his opponents tactics The buglike put his arms forward and
flew blades first at the oncoming Grimlock.
